---
title: Spiced Turkey Tikka with Butternut Squash and Coconut Milk
description: Aromatics are the key to a flavourful tikka. Tonight's turkey tikka is packed with warming spices and sweet squash. Savoury turkey and rich coconut milk balance out this bright, fragrant curry!
